title: Tech companies are gaming out responses to the Texas social media law
description: Social media companies aren't waiting on the Supreme Court to start thinking about how they can respond to a Texas law prohibiting them from removing political speech.

title: If a Google billionaire can’t make flying cars happen, can anyone?
description: A secretive air-taxi startup backed by Google co-founder Larry Page, is winding down, underscoring how difficult it will be to get electric-powered flying cars and planes.
